Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Warblade level 11.
Specifics: You anticipate your enemies' ploys and tactics. At 11th level, you gain a bonus equal to your Intelligence modifier on any check made to oppose an enemy's taunt, feint, or parry attempt.  Additionally, starting with the first round of an encounter, you gain an immunity effect against knockdown which lasts for an amount of rounds equal to your Int modifier (if any).